/* recovery / constant/propertyDict -- F2 property context.

   Inherits the plant context (components, eNRTL config, and the NRTL ethanol-water
   parameter in propertyData/parameters/) and overrides ONLY the liquid method: NRTL
   for the ethanol/water azeotrope, overriding the plant eNRTL.

   The SELECTED liquid method defines the ACTIVE world.  `activity.NRTL` is molecular,
   so the inherited salt chemistry (sylvite / ion speciation) stays AVAILABLE but
   INACTIVE for this liquid -- it is not required by NRTL and never contaminates it.
   Inheritance is explicit (`inherits`, a directory), never `#include`, never a symlink. */
inherits "../../../constant";

propertyMethods
{
    liquid activity.NRTL;
}
